      <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mt-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">现代 API（D3D12/Vulkan）的<b>核心思想</b>：把<b>控制权</b>从驱动交还给应用——应用显式管理内存、同步、PSO，换来可预测的极高吞吐。代价是代码量翻 5-10 倍。游戏引擎（UE5/Unity）封装了这些复杂度，让上层开发者用回 OpenGL 风格的简洁 API。</span><span slot="en">Modern APIs' (D3D12/Vulkan) <b>core idea</b>: hand <b>control</b> back from driver to app — explicit memory, sync, PSO, in exchange for predictable high throughput. The cost is 5-10× more code. Game engines (UE5/Unity) wrap this complexity, exposing an OpenGL-style simple API to upper-layer developers.</span></Bilingual></p>
